data.description: Beautiful two-bedroom town-home, conveniently located off Highway 280 and close to restaurants and schools. This KITCHEN is amazing, with open concept space and a built in coffee bar, great appliances and lighting.along with hardwoods along the main level. Upstairs, stretch out in the large bedrooms, each with their own bathroom. Master bath, has a jetted tub to relax after work! If that not enough , you have bonus space in the basement to expand or escape, along with a rear entrance garage! Schedule your showing, now ,this one will not last! Carpet is fairly new and new toilets in bathrooms. Home is equipped with NEST thermostats and 5G wireless available in area.
